OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fwith evening sunny spells and then
OL,7,Fclear spells overnight. Perhaps the
OL,8,Fodd spot of rain over Kent at first.
OL,9,FTurning a little breezy, but mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FSunny spells for most, but
OL,12,Fisolated showers are possible. Breezy,
OL,13,Fespecially along southern coasts, and
OL,14,Fcooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
